  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  title: "Khung x\u01B0\u01A1ng t\u1EBF b\xE0o"
  description: "B\u1ED9 khung x\u01B0\u01A1ng t\u1EBF b\xE0o l\xE0 h\u1EC7 th\u1ED1ng
    m\u1EA1ng vi s\u1EE3i, s\u1EE3i trung gian v\xE0 vi \u1ED1ng k\u1EBFt n\u1ED1i
    v\u1EDBi nhau. Vai tr\xF2 ch\xEDnh c\u1EE7a b\u1ED9 khung x\u01B0\u01A1ng t\u1EBF
    b\xE0o l\xE0 n\xE2ng \u0111\u1EE1, duy tr\xEC h\xECnh d\u1EA1ng t\u1EBF b\xE0o,
    neo gi\u1EEF b\xE0o quan v\xE0 c\xE1c enzyme, h\xECnh th\xE0nh n\xEAn trung th\u1EC3
    c\xF3 vai tr\xF2 trong qu\xE1 tr\xECnh ph\xE2n b\xE0o, h\u1ED7 tr\u1EE3 c\xE1c
    b\u1ED9 ph\u1EADn hay c\u1EA3 t\u1EBF b\xE0o di chuy\u1EC3n.\r"
