  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  title: "T\u1EBF b\xE0o ch\u1EA5t"
  description: "Kh\u1ED1i t\u1EBF b\xE0o ch\u1EA5t ch\u1EE9a 65 \u2013 90 % n\u01B0\u1EDBc
    c\xF9ng c\xE1c ch\u1EA5t v\xF4 c\u01A1 v\xE0 h\u1EEFu c\u01A1 kh\xE1c nhau. \u0110\xE2y
    l\xE0 b\xE0o quan duy nh\u1EA5t \u1EDF t\u1EBF b\xE0o nh\xE2n s\u01A1, ch\xFAng
    kh\xF4ng c\xF3 m\xE0ng bao b\u1ECDc. T\u1EBF b\xE0o ch\u1EA5t l\xE0 n\u01A1i
    di\u1EC5n ra c\xE1c ph\u1EA3n \u1EE9ng sinh ho\xE1, \u0111\u1EA3m b\u1EA3o duy
    tr\xEC ho\u1EA1t \u0111\u1ED9ng s\u1ED1ng c\u1EE7a t\u1EBF b\xE0o.\r"
  pathType: 0
  partId: 6
  icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 333a06d240c09344a8ebf1326efd1f6b, type: 3}
