  title: Peroxisome
  description: "L\xE0 b\xE0o quan c\xF3 d\u1EA1ng h\xECnh c\u1EA7u, \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
    bao b\u1ECDc b\u1EDFi m\u1ED9t m\xE0ng \u0111\u01A1n m\u1ECFng v\xE0 th\u01B0\u1EDDng
    n\u1EB1m g\u1EA7n l\u01B0\u1EDBi n\u1ED9i ch\u1EA5t. B\xEAn trong peroxysome
    ch\u1EE9a c\xE1c enzyme c\xF3 kh\u1EA3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1EC3n hydro t\u1EEB nhi\u1EC1u
    ch\u1EA5t kh\xE1c nhau, nh\u01B0 c\xE1c ch\u1EA5t \u0111\u1ED9c ho\u1EB7c alcohol,
    sang oxy \u0111\u1EC3 t\u1EA1o th\xE0nh hydrogen peroxide (H2O2), sau \u0111\xF3
    c\xE1c enzyme kh\xE1c s\u1EBD ph\xE2n gi\u1EA3i H2O2 th\xE0nh n\u01B0\u1EDBc
    v\xE0 oxy, gi\xFAp b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 t\u1EBF b\xE0o kh\u1ECFi \u0111\u1ED9c t\xEDnh.
    \u1EDE th\u1EF1c v\u1EADt, m\u1ED9t lo\u1EA1i peroxysome \u0111\u1EB7c bi\u1EC7t
    g\u1ECDi l\xE0 glioxysome ch\u1EE9a enzyme x\xFAc t\xE1c ph\u1EA3n \u1EE9ng ph\xE2n
    t\xE1ch c\xE1c acid b\xE9o th\xE0nh acetyl-CoA, ch\u1EA5t n\xE0y \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
    chuy\u1EC3n \u0111\u1EBFn ty th\u1EC3 \u0111\u1EC3 tham gia v\xE0o qu\xE1 tr\xECnh
    h\xF4 h\u1EA5p t\u1EBF b\xE0o. Nh\u1EDD \u0111\xF3, peroxysome \u0111\u1EA3m
    nhi\u1EC7m c\xE1c ch\u1EE9c n\u0103ng quan tr\u1ECDng nh\u01B0 ph\xE2n gi\u1EA3i
    H2O2 v\xE0 chuy\u1EC3n h\xF3a lipid trong t\u1EBF b\xE0o.\r"
  pathType: 2
  partId: 6
  icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bbacd89c26c8a6140ad36f0f1b47b130, type: 3}
