  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  title: "M\xE0ng sinh ch\u1EA5t"
  description: "B\xEAn d\u01B0\u1EDBi th\xE0nh t\u1EBF b\xE0o l\xE0 m\xE0ng sinh
    ch\u1EA5t, \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c c\u1EA5u t\u1EA1o t\u1EEB l\u1EDBp k\xE9p phospholipid
    v\xE0 protein. M\xE0ng sinh ch\u1EA5t c\xF3 ch\u1EE9c n\u0103ng ki\u1EC3m so\xE1t
    qu\xE1 tr\xECnh v\u1EADn chuy\u1EC3n c\xE1c ch\u1EA5t ra v\xE0 v\xE0o t\u1EBF
    b\xE0o. Ngo\xE0i ra, m\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 qu\xE1 tr\xECnh chuy\u1EC3n ho\xE1 v\u1EADt
    ch\u1EA5t v\xE0 n\u0103ng l\u01B0\u1EE3ng c\u1EE7a t\u1EBF b\xE0o c\u0169ng di\u1EC5n
    ra tr\xEAn m\xE0ng sinh ch\u1EA5t."
  pathType: 0
  partId: 5
  icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 97f1804afe1173a449523c6ac4d00838, type: 3}
