  description: "\u1EDE nhi\u1EC1u t\u1EBF b\xE0o vi khu\u1EA9n, ngo\xE0i ph\xE2n
    t\u1EED DNA \u1EDF v\xF9ng nh\xE2n c\xF2n c\xF3 m\u1ED9t ho\u1EB7c m\u1ED9t s\u1ED1
    ph\xE2n t\u1EED DNA v\xF2ng, nh\u1ECF g\u1ECDi l\xE0 plasmid. Ch\u1EE9a gene
    h\u1ED7 tr\u1EE3 cho s\u1EF1 sinh tr\u01B0\u1EDFng c\u1EE7a vi khu\u1EA9n (VD:
    gene kh\xE1ng sinh)."
